.col-xs-4.col-xs-offset-3.page-centered
  .wellified.text-center
    = bootstrap_flash
    %h1 Your hacker profile
    %p Do you hack hardware? Build up your hacker identity all in one place and show the world what you're up to.
    %p.cta Be the first to get in:
    = simple_form_for @invite_request, html: { class: 'form-inline' } do |f|
      .row
        = f.input :email, autofocus: true, required: false, placeholder: 'nikola@tesla.com', label: false, wrapper_html: { class: 'col-xs-9' }
        = f.button :submit, "I'm awesome", class: 'btn btn-info col-xs-3'
      %p.help-block We'll send the invite to that address. No spam, promise.